" target=\\\"_blank\\\">2005-2006 Music Visual Performing Arts Funding Award (pdf)</a> (2005-11-10)\r\n<tr><td><a href=\\\"http://www.lpef.org/portal.php?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lpef.org%2Flocal%2F2005-06YardDuty1.pdf&what=T_Links&rid=05/11/10/4065853\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">2005-2006 Yard Duty Funding Award (pdf)</a> (2005-11-10)\r\n</table>',NULL,'Lydia Dobyns','lydia@dobyns.com','',1,202,'2005-11-10 09:38:50',20071113180424,'2005-11-10 09:38:50');
INSERT INTO `T_Stories` VALUES ('06/01/16/2503084','Y',NULL,'198.144.199.78','21','Endowment and Sponsorship Committee Launched','LPEF recently launched a new committee focusing on creating an endowment fund and soliciting business sponsorships for the annual fundraising.','Co-Chairs Charlotte Khandelwal and Lauri Vaughan are enthusiastic about this new function within LPEF.  They are developing a fully-coordinated sponsorship program in which local businesses may participate.  The committee intends to explore endowments as well.  Volunteers are welcomed to help Charlotte and Lauri develop sponsorship connections.  Charlotte Khandelway can be contacted at 353-4530 and Lauri Vaughan can be contacted at 353-1666. ',NULL,'Peggy Johnson','mtj@selfridge.com','',1,235,'2006-01-16 15:15:03',20071116114012,'2006-01-16 15:15:03');
INSERT INTO `T_Stories` VALUES ('06/02/28/6907677','Y',NULL,'64.74.213.74','22','2007 Gala Tickets On Sale Now','The 2007 LPEF Gala, \\\"Under a Starry Sky\\\" will be held on Satuarday, October 6, 2007 at Maison du Lac. We encourage you to buy your tickets now as this event has sold out each year. You won\\\'t want to miss out on a great evening which benefits all children in the Loma Prieta Joint Union School District.','The 2007 LPEF Gala, \\\"Under a Starry Sky\\\" will be held on October 6, 2007 at Maison du Lac.  We encourage you to buy your tickets now as this event has sold out each year. Download the <b><u><a href=\\\"http://www.lpef.org/local/2007%20Gala%20ticket%20order.pdf\\\">2007 ticket order form</a></u></b>. You won\\\'t want to miss out on a great evening which benefits all children in the Loma Prieta Joint Union School District.  We have received exciting items for the auction and look forward to working with the many volunteers who have come forward to help this year!  \r\n\r\nJennifer Straw and Gretchen Goosey are the 2007 gala co-chairs. Mary Ashley, Julie Bourque, and Jennifer Katinsky are also on the gala committee. More volunteers are needed to help produce this fun event. If you would like to help, or have an item to donate to the auction, call Jennifer Straw, 408-353-8981.',NULL,'Jennifer Straw','jenniferstraw@comcast.net','',1,573,'2007-05-01 18:51:06',20071116121347,'2006-02-28 23:21:47');
INSERT INTO `T_Stories` VALUES ('06/02/28/8887037','N',NULL,'64.74.213.74','20','2006-2007 Keep Campaign','LPEF is working with the Home & School Clubs in a coordinated year-long fundraising effort.','LPEF is again working with the Home & School Clubs in a coordinated year-long fundraising effort. The KEEP committee members include Pat McGrath (Co-chair), Diane Matlock (Co-chair), Henry Castaniada, Joann Colombo, Lydia Dobyns, Melanie Earhart, Diana Hallock, Charlotte Khandelwal, Paula Lacey, and Lauri Vaughan.  ',NULL,'Peggy Johnson','mtj@selfridge.com','',1,133,'2006-02-28 23:54:47',20071113180431,'2006-02-28 23:54:47');
