 and Performing Arts saved next year. The next KEEP priority identified is technology upgrades; any additional funds received before June 30th will go towards the technology program award.\r\n\r\nThank you again for your fantastic support!\r\n\r\n<b>The KEEP Campaign Committee:</b>\r\n \r\n<pre>\r\nPat McGrath, Chair\r\nHenry Castaniada\r\nJoAnn Colombo\r\nLydia Dobyns\r\nMelanie Earhart\r\nCharlotte Boisvert-Khandelwal\r\nPaula Lacey\r\nDiane Matlock\r\nLauri Vaughan\r\n</pre>',NULL,'Lydia Dobyns','lydia@dobyns.com','',1,261,'2006-06-10 19:18:13',20071116112453,'2006-06-10 19:13:21');
